Simulation Parameters
| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|--------|
| Number of Customers | 106 |
| Queue Capacity | 106 |
| Service Capacity | 1 |
| Arrival Type | Rate |
| Service Time | Triangular Distribution |

Results
- Successfully simulated **106 customers**.
- All customers completed the service process.
- Average queue length remained low.
- No customers remained in the system at the end of the simulation.

